!doctype html
%main
  %h1 uugnet mesh pages
  %p super tiny site server using hand-written .msh files.
  %p
    %a(href="/wiki/") open the wiki
  %ul
    %li
      %a(href="/wiki/rf-notes") rf notes
    %li
      %a(href="/scratchpad") scratchpad (create scratchpad.msh)
  %p(class="muted") tip: urls without extension will resolve to .msh files.

